137
00:21:28,540 --> 00:21:30,451
Thursday, 27. of July :

138
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:33,775
A very hot and hazy day.

139
00:21:34,940 --> 00:21:37,170
I still feel bad from my illness.

140
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:46,939
Do you see this mark ?

141
00:22:48,780 --> 00:22:50,850
Be careful, my dear.

142
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:53,336
Or it will end in disasterl.

143
00:22:54,300 --> 00:22:55,574
Don't you remember?

144
00:22:55,860 --> 00:22:58,818
I was going to a party
and was wearing by green robe.

145
00:22:59,260 --> 00:23:02,252
Afterwards it was difficult to set up
my hair again.

146
00:23:03,100 --> 00:23:04,692
Then I forgot my gloves.

147
00:23:07,860 --> 00:23:09,657
I have to speak to you about
something.

148
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:14,896
I need to show you a letter I got.

149
00:23:16,060 --> 00:23:17,334
It was sent yesterday.

150
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:19,575
Here's how it goes.

151
00:23:21,020 --> 00:23:24,057
"You don't see us,
but we see you.

152
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:27,016
"Horrible things
can happen.

153
00:23:27,620 --> 00:23:29,770
"Dreams can
become real.

154
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,691
"The end is near.

155
00:23:33,980 --> 00:23:35,971
"Tears will dry up.

156
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:40,288
"Other liquids will wet
your white clothes.

157
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:42,411
This has been decided.

158
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:47,096
I almost felt ill reading it.

159
00:23:50,860 --> 00:23:52,816
How warm your hands are !

160
00:23:53,460 --> 00:23:54,734
Do you have a fever ?

161
00:23:59,620 --> 00:24:03,499
Always when I'm going to meet you,
I'm so troubled.

162
00:24:05,580 --> 00:24:08,777
I walk around like in a
dream all afternoon.

163
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:13,449
Everything is unreal, meaningless.

164
00:24:19,140 --> 00:24:21,176
Help me with the zipper of my robe, please.

165
00:24:21,700 --> 00:24:23,736
It always gets hooked up.

166
00:25:14,660 --> 00:25:17,936
I blows a lot,
but it is splendid, don't you think ?

167
00:25:19,020 --> 00:25:21,295
Perfect for a painter.

168
00:25:22,020 --> 00:25:24,375
You have been living here
for quite some time.

169
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:26,696
You return to the scene
of the crime, so to speak !

170
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:28,697
To commit new crimes.

171
00:25:29,180 --> 00:25:31,694
You look tired.
Do not exhaust yourself.

172
00:25:31,940 --> 00:25:34,579
At your age, be careful.

173
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:37,095
The young are more robust.

174
00:25:37,780 --> 00:25:41,568
I know what I'm talking about.
My name is Hebrandt, curator.

175
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:46,050
I'm examining the souls.
And what do you get to see ?

176
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:50,329
I won't teach you anything.
You're an artist.

177
00:25:50,820 --> 00:25:54,699
You do it in your facial studies ,
not to speak of your self-portaits.

178
00:25:55,260 --> 00:25:58,650
Why do you look at me like that ?
Do you hurt ? Are you nervous ?

179
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,134
Anything bothering you ?

180
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:04,016
Shut up !

181
