267
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,418
he cries in despair :

268
00:36:30,620 --> 00:36:33,692
O eternal night,
when do you end ?

269
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:37,930
When will light
again touch my eyes ?

270
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:43,494
The deadly ill Mozart,
knows the intensity of these words.

271
00:36:44,980 --> 00:36:47,130
And the choir responds :

272
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:51,649
Soon,
young man, or never !

273
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:57,294
The most beautiful
and troubling music

274
00:36:57,500 --> 00:37:00,378
ever composed.

275
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:03,769
Tamino asks :

276
00:37:04,540 --> 00:37:06,258
Does Pamina still live ?

277
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:09,611
The invisible choir responds :

278
00:37:10,340 --> 00:37:12,808
Pamina still lives !

279
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:20,577
Listen to the strange, ingenious
partition of the syllables.

280
00:37:31,540 --> 00:37:33,690
This is no longer
the name of a young woman,

281
00:37:35,140 --> 00:37:36,812
it is a magic formula,

282
00:37:37,340 --> 00:37:38,773
an incantation.

283
00:37:39,820 --> 00:37:42,937
A naive text, a commanded work,

284
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:46,818
And yet the highest
manifestation of art.

285
00:37:47,020 --> 00:37:48,817
What do you think Mr. Artist ?

286
00:37:50,140 --> 00:37:54,053
Excuse me. I call myself artist,
short of a better word.

287
00:37:54,820 --> 00:37:57,539
In my creative work,
nothing is evident,

288
00:37:57,740 --> 00:37:58,934
rather it is a compulsion.

289
00:37:59,540 --> 00:38:03,294
Without me wanting it, I have
been classified as something "exceptional",

290
00:38:04,020 --> 00:38:06,090
5-legged calf, monster.

291
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:07,978
I have never fought for
that position,

292
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:10,740
nor am I fighting to keep it.

293
00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:15,173
Sure enough, I have felt
megalomania lick my forehead

294
00:38:15,980 --> 00:38:17,538
but I believe I am immune.

295
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,856
It is sufficient to think
about the small importance

296
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:22,972
of art
in today's world.

297
00:38:23,660 --> 00:38:27,653
To cool down.
Yet my compulsion remains.

298
00:38:28,740 --> 00:38:30,173
What an artist !

299
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:33,850
What bravery !
How clear-minded !

300
00:38:34,100 --> 00:38:37,490
I want to propose a toast to our,
not just a genious,

301
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:40,009
but an equally strong thinker !

302
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:42,536
A rose in your hair...

303
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:46,856
Oh ! I scrathed you with my nail !

304
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:50,018
You're bleeding. Here, my handkerchief.

305
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:55,409
It is clean. How could I be so clumsy ?

306
00:38:59,020 --> 00:39:02,808
Relax. You have drunk too much. Come be with me now.

307
00:39:03,860 --> 00:39:06,294
He has insomnia,
that's why he can't take much alcohol.

308
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:08,456
Let us get some air on the terrace.

309
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:15,013
The core of the castle
is from the 14th century.

310
00:39:15,860 --> 00:39:18,294
It has been in our family
since the end of the 15th.

311
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:21,890
We were a bit elated back there,
it is because we live so isolated.

312
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:25,212
We scared you.
But you won't leave us now ?

313
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:28,412
Look, Corinne, our
castle looks nice this time of night.

314
00:39:28,620 --> 00:39:29,689
At night, yes.

315
00:39:30,540 --> 00:39:34,738
Oh ! My stocking ! Turn away Mr. Hebrand.

316
00:39:34,940 --> 00:39:37,170
Where were you, Ernst ?
Where did you walk ?

317
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:39,211
I took a different path.

318
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:42,014
I'm ashamed that
our park has been neglected.

319
00:39:42,420 --> 00:39:45,253
19 years ago,
it was a paragon of parks !

320
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:48,020
We never kiss eachother, did you think about that ?

321
00:39:49,220 --> 00:39:51,529
I can almost count our kisses.

322
00:39:51,780 --> 00:39:53,975
One thing scares me innsanely.

323
00:39:54,780 --> 00:39:56,736
I meet a stranger on the road.

324
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,931
We talk about various things.

325
00:39:59,500 --> 00:40:02,856
Suddenly he turns around,
and strikes me on the cheek.

326
00:40:03,620 --> 00:40:06,930
His face and eyes filled with hatred.

327
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:10,937
I don't understand a thing,
my nose is bleeding.

328
00:40:11,300 --> 00:40:14,610
I stutter some excuses...

329
00:40:16,020 --> 00:40:18,011
and I ask myself
when he has disappeared.

330
00:40:18,220 --> 00:40:20,529
Is it like that ?
Does it have to be like that ?

331
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:23,859
I can never forget the man's eyes...

332
00:40:33,860 --> 00:40:35,213
Are you leaving already ?

333
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:39,417
Before you leave you must see
where I put the painting of Veronica Vogler.

334
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:41,378
Alma dear, come with us.

335
00:40:41,620 --> 00:40:43,531
She is asleep.
We must not disturb here.

336
00:40:43,740 --> 00:40:45,173
No , I'm not asleep.

337
00:40:45,380 --> 00:40:46,699
You want to leave ?

338
00:40:46,940 --> 00:40:49,090
Come both of you.

339
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:54,449
Alma, now you will see something
beautiful created by your husband.

340
00:40:55,300 --> 00:40:58,337
There it is. Opposite my bed.

341
00:40:59,260 --> 00:41:01,216
I watch it morning and evening.

342
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:04,655
It is a part of my solitude.

343
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:09,689
I love her.

344
00:41:14,420 --> 00:41:16,490
Were you together
for a long time ?

345
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:18,497
Pardon my indiscretion.

346
00:41:19,260 --> 00:41:20,488
5 years.

347
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:22,735
Oh ! He told you !

348
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:25,333
He loved her, didn't he ?

349
00:41:26,300 --> 00:41:27,813
I don't have to ask that.

350
00:41:29,540 --> 00:41:33,613
Quite a scandal at the time.
But how romantic !

351
00:41:35,420 --> 00:41:36,250
Jealous ?

352
00:41:37,100 --> 00:41:37,691
I don't think so.

353
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:41,850
My husband is jealous.
But an excellent lover !

354
00:41:43,660 --> 00:41:45,491
Look at this mark.

355
00:41:46,460 --> 00:41:49,736
Form another man's "advances"

356
00:41:50,220 --> 00:41:52,780
An eternal source of excitement.

357
00:41:54,940 --> 00:41:56,931
Trivial, of course,

358
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:59,018
but stimulating for me !

359
00:41:59,380 --> 00:42:00,893
But I will have to find
something else.

360
00:42:01,100 --> 00:42:04,058
This mark is not
sufficient forever.

361
00:42:04,380 --> 00:42:07,816
Will you help me please ?
Don't be angry, Alma, please.

362
00:42:08,420 --> 00:42:12,459
I'm joking !
Silly, wasn't it ?

363
00:42:12,660 --> 00:42:14,412
Let us join the others.

364
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:23,330
I have purchased a significant
part of your husband !

365
00:42:25,180 --> 00:42:26,408
Don't you think ?

366
00:42:47,660 --> 00:42:51,494
I want to tell you :
I have read your diary.

367
00:42:52,620 --> 00:42:54,656
It filled me with fear.
No, let me finish.

368
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:57,694
I want you to hear
what I've been thinking these days.

369
00:42:58,060 --> 00:42:59,095
Here it goes...

370
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:02,379
I can see something terrible happening,

371
00:43:02,740 --> 00:43:04,492
undefinable...

372
00:43:05,620 --> 00:43:07,815
But dont think
I will run away.

373
00:43:08,500 --> 00:43:11,458
I won't run despite my fear.

374
00:43:12,940 --> 00:43:14,658
One more thing:
They want to separate us.

375
00:43:15,020 --> 00:43:20,299
They want you. As long as I'm with
you, it is harder.

376
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:27,458
Johan, you can't make me
run away, however much you try.

377
00:43:28,420 --> 00:43:30,980
I'm staying...

378
00:43:32,340 --> 00:43:34,331
Johan, answer me !

379
00:44:19,340 --> 00:44:22,298
THE HOUR OF THE WOLF

380
00:45:04,900 --> 00:45:05,935
Listen to the silence ?

381
00:45:14,340 --> 00:45:17,810
There was a time when
nights were for sleeping...

382
00:45:19,300 --> 00:45:21,450
deeply, without dreams.

383
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:26,055
To sleep, and awake without fear.

384
00:45:32,500 --> 00:45:33,330
Tired ?

385
00:45:34,260 --> 00:45:35,978
Not yet.

386
00:45:36,820 --> 00:45:39,288
We've been avake until dawn,
every night.

387
00:45:42,900 --> 00:45:44,936
But this hour is the hardest.

388
00:45:48,180 --> 00:45:49,408
Do you know it's name ?

389
00:45:51,260 --> 00:45:53,820
The old ones called it
"the hour of the wolf".

390
00:45:54,780 --> 00:45:56,816
It is the hour when
the most people die,

391
00:45:57,740 --> 00:45:59,617
and the most are born.

392
00:46:00,300 --> 00:46:02,291
At this time,
nightmares come to us.

393
00:46:04,140 --> 00:46:05,095
And when we awake...

394
00:46:05,300 --> 00:46:06,449
We are afraid.

395
00:46:07,940 --> 00:46:08,929
We are afraid.

396
00:46:15,220 --> 00:46:16,050
What is it ?

397
00:46:17,020 --> 00:46:20,092
Nothing. I was thinking about
something from my childhood.

398
00:46:23,180 --> 00:46:25,011
A form of punishment.

399
00:46:26,180 --> 00:46:28,136
I was thrown in the wardrobe,
the door was closed.

400
00:46:28,980 --> 00:46:32,177
Without any sound, in the dark.

401
00:46:33,820 --> 00:46:37,369
I was insanely scared and
pounded the door.

402
00:46:38,340 --> 00:46:42,128
They had told me
a small person lived in the wardrobe,

403
00:46:44,260 --> 00:46:47,935
who could bite away the toes
of bad children.

404
00:46:49,860 --> 00:46:54,251
When I stopped the pounding,
I could hear a sound in a corner...

405
00:46:55,140 --> 00:46:57,495
I believed my time had come.

406
00:46:57,940 --> 00:47:01,012
In panic, I started climbing

407
00:47:01,540 --> 00:47:04,100
inside the wardrobe.

408
00:47:05,100 --> 00:47:09,776
On shoeboxes and shelves,
I tried to lift myself up by the hands.

409
00:47:10,180 --> 00:47:11,932
I lost my grip and fell.

410
00:47:12,380 --> 00:47:16,498
I fought wildly to keep the 
creature off me...

411
00:47:17,860 --> 00:47:20,613
and all the time
screaming with fear...

412
00:47:21,820 --> 00:47:23,458
asking forgiveness !

413
00:47:24,660 --> 00:47:27,333
Finally the door opened
and I was allowed to come out...

414
00:47:28,380 --> 00:47:29,210
in the light.

415
00:47:31,700 --> 00:47:36,137
My father says :
"Your mother assures me you ask for pardon."

416
00:47:37,380 --> 00:47:40,656
I shout : "Yes I do !"

417
00:47:42,260 --> 00:47:45,138
"Let's go to the sofa then", he said to me.

418
00:47:46,300 --> 00:47:48,530
I went to the green sofa 
in my father's room,

419
00:47:49,460 --> 00:47:53,692
took a couple of cushions,
put them on top of eachother

420
00:47:55,460 --> 00:47:58,736
I then fetched the stick,
unbuttoned my pants,

421
00:47:58,940 --> 00:48:01,215
and lay myself over the cushions.

422
00:48:03,060 --> 00:48:07,497
My father said :
"How many strikes did you earn ?"

423
00:48:09,220 --> 00:48:12,371
I answered : "The maximum."

424
00:48:14,060 --> 00:48:15,732
Then he beat me,

425
00:48:16,500 --> 00:48:19,651
hard, but bearable.

426
00:48:24,020 --> 00:48:27,217
After the punishement,
I turned towards my mother

427
00:48:27,940 --> 00:48:31,091
and asked her : "Can you forgive me now ?"

428
00:48:32,220 --> 00:48:36,657
She cried and said :
"Sure I forgive you."

429
00:48:39,860 --> 00:48:41,657
She gave me her hand,

430
00:48:43,580 --> 00:48:44,979
I kissed it...

431
00:48:56,540 --> 00:48:58,337
Are you sleeping ?

432
00:48:59,180 --> 00:49:00,852
No, I'm not sleeping.

433
00:49:02,740 --> 00:49:04,219
My back aches.

434
00:49:07,060 --> 00:49:09,415
All the pain still...

435
00:49:11,460 --> 00:49:12,859
How quiet it is.

436
00:49:14,620 --> 00:49:17,180
Strange when..
the ocean is calm and quiet

437
00:49:18,620 --> 00:49:21,453
Eerie in a way.

438
00:49:22,460 --> 00:49:23,415
Are you crying ?

439
00:49:26,980 --> 00:49:28,493
No, I'm thinking about the child.

440
00:49:29,860 --> 00:49:32,215
And of the big silent darkness,

441
00:49:33,340 --> 00:49:35,729
as if the day
will never come back.

442
00:49:36,540 --> 00:49:37,893
Poor you.

443
00:49:39,820 --> 00:49:41,219
Give me your hand.

444
00:49:43,900 --> 00:49:45,299
That is better.

445
00:49:50,900 --> 00:49:54,051
Do you remember when I came home 
and told you I was bitten by a serpent ?

446
00:49:58,220 --> 00:49:59,938
It was no serpent.

447
00:50:05,780 --> 00:50:08,613
I was thinking I would never
tell anyone.

448
00:50:10,020 --> 00:50:11,294
Tell me.

449
00:50:12,540 --> 00:50:14,178
You must never tell anyone.

450
00:50:15,740 --> 00:50:17,412
No, I promise.

451
00:50:18,740 --> 00:50:20,651
You remember the place
where the water is deep ?

452
00:50:20,940 --> 00:50:22,817
We were there sometimes 
in the beginning of summer.

453
00:56:32,620 --> 00:56:34,019
Did you lock the door well ?

454
00:56:34,620 --> 00:56:35,769
I checked it twice.

455
00:56:46,980 --> 00:56:50,211
Good morning.
Pardon me for disturbing you.

456
00:56:51,620 --> 00:56:54,737
It looks like there will be a storm.
I thought I would make a visit...

457
00:56:56,100 --> 00:56:57,658
I have a message too.

458
00:56:59,300 --> 00:57:01,860
May I sit down ? I won't be long.

459
00:57:06,340 --> 00:57:07,898
There is an invitation
from the castle.

460
00:57:08,100 --> 00:57:09,818
We are having a small party.

461
00:57:10,020 --> 00:57:13,376
Nothing big, just us
pitiful people

462
00:57:13,580 --> 00:57:17,368
enjoying eachothers company.

463
00:57:18,340 --> 00:57:22,299
One of the invited will interest you.

464
00:57:23,100 --> 00:57:26,092
Veronica Vogler.
She is coming. Are you ?

465
00:57:27,220 --> 00:57:30,337
Good. We will see you then.

466
00:57:33,380 --> 00:57:35,257
One more thing...
Von Merkens and I

467
00:57:35,460 --> 00:57:37,530
have discussed how to defend you..

468
00:57:38,140 --> 00:57:40,654
from the little dangers 
on this island.

469
00:57:43,500 --> 00:57:46,333
That is all for now. 
See you later my friends.

470
00:57:46,620 --> 00:57:48,656
Hope to see you at our party.

471
00:57:54,620 --> 00:57:56,292
Wont you lock away your weapons ?

472
00:57:56,860 --> 00:57:58,054
No, why ?

473
00:58:02,300 --> 00:58:04,177
What shall we do today ?

474
00:58:06,180 --> 00:58:08,296
Talk to me about Veronica Vogler.

475
00:58:13,340 --> 00:58:16,650
What can I say ? It went on for 5 years.

476
00:58:17,820 --> 00:58:21,176
You already know. It was discovered,
it was a big scandal.

477
00:58:21,380 --> 00:58:24,292
Then it was hushed down.
That was the end of it.

478
00:58:25,060 --> 00:58:27,051
This is not what it says in
your diary.

479
00:58:34,820 --> 00:58:38,130
"My obsession with Veronica
became a torment to us both.

480
00:58:38,620 --> 00:58:41,976
"I  followed her around,
spying, in jealousy.

481
00:58:42,500 --> 00:58:45,060
"My suffering was stimulating for her,
I think,

482
00:58:45,260 --> 00:58:47,410
"but she was passive and indecisive.

483
00:58:47,900 --> 00:58:49,811
"There were some 
frightening scenes,

484
00:58:50,020 --> 00:58:52,170
"without sense or reason.

485
00:58:53,380 --> 00:58:55,132
"We traveled from town to town,

486
00:58:55,340 --> 00:58:57,649
"to avoid her relatives and their lawyers..."

487
00:59:04,420 --> 00:59:06,490
"We certainly lived by
the word of the Bible :

488
00:59:06,700 --> 00:59:09,817
"Of man and woman as one flesh.

489
00:59:10,980 --> 00:59:13,016
"Then her husband came to get her.

490
00:59:13,500 --> 00:59:15,297
"I was taken to hospital.

491
00:59:15,780 --> 00:59:17,611
"We did not see eachother for 
several years."

492
00:59:24,420 --> 00:59:28,857
You once said to me 
what you liked about me was,

493
00:59:30,140 --> 00:59:32,574
I was conceived as one piece
by God.

494
00:59:36,860 --> 00:59:39,499
That my thoughts and
feelings are whole .

495
00:59:42,180 --> 00:59:45,650
You said it is important
that there are people like me.

496
00:59:49,140 --> 00:59:51,096
I thought that sounded so nice.

497
00:59:52,580 --> 00:59:54,013
I was so happy.

498
00:59:56,660 --> 00:59:57,934
I was wrong.

499
01:00:00,620 --> 01:00:01,848
I understand nothing.

500
01:00:05,660 --> 01:00:08,493
I understand nothing.
I don't understand you.

501
01:00:10,060 --> 01:00:11,857
I'm just afraid.

502
01:00:13,580 --> 01:00:17,459
Do you think I want to stay
here, risking being beat to death ?

503
01:00:19,340 --> 01:00:22,696
Do you think I want to see
you running after that woman ?

504
01:00:22,900 --> 01:00:26,449
Talking to your phantoms,
do you think I want to ?

505
01:00:29,820 --> 01:00:30,411
But I stay.

506
01:01:17,620 --> 01:01:19,258
Rise up from the table.

507
01:01:29,620 --> 01:01:31,053
Go to the door.

508
01:01:34,780 --> 01:01:35,769
Go outside.

509
01:01:37,220 --> 01:01:38,539
Go dow the stairs.
It is no longer dark.

510
01:01:39,020 --> 01:01:40,612
You can see clear.

511
01:02:07,020 --> 01:02:10,695
What a surprise !

512
01:02:11,660 --> 01:02:14,732
Carry these plates for me please.

513
01:02:15,060 --> 01:02:17,699
Thank you.
This is my night-table you see.

514
01:02:18,940 --> 01:02:22,853
Lindhorst, who knows the worlds,
says old trollops 

515
01:02:23,060 --> 01:02:25,733
develop an insatiable appetite !

516
01:02:28,380 --> 01:02:29,972
Do you really not want anything ?

517
01:02:30,580 --> 01:02:31,899
Isn't there a party here tonight ?

518
01:02:32,740 --> 01:02:34,173
As far as I know, yes.

519
01:02:36,940 --> 01:02:38,931
Don't leave !

520
01:02:41,900 --> 01:02:44,095
Help me with my stockings, please.

521
01:02:46,860 --> 01:02:48,612
You like touching me.

522
01:02:49,580 --> 01:02:51,093
I can feel it.

523
01:02:52,260 --> 01:02:54,296
I don't understand you !

524
01:02:55,580 --> 01:02:57,730
Veronica Vogler has arrived.

525
01:02:59,740 --> 01:03:02,129
Only I can tell you
